claim: Flublok ensures identical antigenic match with WHO- and FDA-selected flu strains.
explanation: A table listing demographic and clinical characteristics of study participants by vaccine group (Flublok vs standard-dose and combined), including number of participants, sex distribution, racial and ethnic groups, preexisting illnesses, and prior influenza vaccination history. The table provides only participant demographics and clinical characteristics and does not present any information on antigenic matching to WHO- or FDA-selected flu strains, and therefore does not support the claim. Note: None
